{"tid":1478966,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[粵塾請人喇！] 想請一個marketing analysts 幫手推廣我哋嘅品牌同廣東話電子書","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T04:05:44.000Z","uid":223799,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"805d340009b0ed4dd8adea11ad3f07e099210fd5","tid":1478966,"uid":223799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wjg8SRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjg8SRM.jpg&h=51a8c5a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抱住向世界推廣廣東話同香港文化嘅使命，粵塾（How to study Cantonese）係一間專門出版廣東話電子書同有聲書嘅公司。我哋嘅目標顧客係嚟自英語系國家、學𡁵廣東話嘅外國人同海外港人。我哋嘅團隊由擁有唔同專長（設計、插畫、配音、動畫、網頁設計、小編、廣東話文法）嘅巴絲（94-97）組成。經過大概10個月嘅努力，我哋開始建立到我哋嘅品牌同有revenue。<br />\n<br />\n我哋依家想請一個marketing analysts 幫手發展我哋嘅品牌。呢一個職位主要負責分析數據，做我哋嘅mastermind，決定我哋marketing 上面嘅發展方向。我哋會另外有人負責執行同development。<br />\n<br />\n職責：<br />\n- 建立同定期更新measurement plan，幫我哋達成我哋嘅Business objectives（每個月檢討同更新一次）<br />\n- 分析Google Analytic, Facebook Pixel, Facebook Page同其他類似service嘅數據，幫我哋嘅content, web design 同其他有關嘅嘢提供建議（每星期一次）。<br />\n- 幫手決定公司嘅marketing嘅發展方向<br />\n<br />\n酬勞：<br />\n- 我哋Ebook revenue 嘅 10~15% <br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣，就用telegram或者Facebook聯絡我哋啦：<a href=\"https://t.me/fargohighfly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffargohighfly&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0dE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=7a6f985b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fargohighfly</a> <br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅Facebook page: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/howtostudycantonese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhowtostudycantonese&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0dE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=e5160d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/howtostudycantonese</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅網站: <a href=\"http://www.howtostudycantonese.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtostudycantonese.com&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0dE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=c027a367\" data